Time Train No. Print this PageShanghai - Nanjing Train Schedule DepartingtoFrom As two of the most important cities in East China, Shanghai and Nanjing are close to each other and linked with each other by the well-developed rail network. It is very convenient to get to Nanjing from Shanghai as there are many trains going to Nanjing every day. Passengers can choose to take a train to Nanjing at Shanghai Hongqiao Railway Station or Shanghai Railway Station. As for more details, passengers can see Shanghai-Nanjing train schedule on China Highlights. China Highlights provides Shanghai-Nanjing train schedule for you to search fro a train from Shanghai to Nanjing.
